data.meta_description:
139 likes, 0 comments - mytmgroup on March 14, 2024: "#TMNews⁣
⁣
Unifi Business through a strategic partnership with Teleme Technologies, is proud to introduce the e-Pharmacy Solution, a mobile application to reshape the landscape of pharmacy services. ⁣
⁣
The service includes access to over 500 licensed healthcare professionals to enhance patient care, streamline prescription processing, and ensure secure medication management. The solution aims to aid pharmacists in providing essential medications and pharmaceutical services, especially in rural and underserved communities where access to healthcare may be limited.⁣
⁣
Amar Huzaimi Md Deris, our Group CEO, highlighted "This new offering reflects TM’s continuous efforts towards becoming a Digital Powerhouse by 2030, leading industry growth through digitalisation and sustainability, and strengthening our digital ecosystem to benefit communities and businesses."⁣
⁣
Click a link in our bio to read more!⁣
⁣
#TM #YourNextIsNow #PWR2030".
